Class
Description
Basketball
Basketball is a Game with the unique Sport enum identifier being set to BASKETBALL
Football
Football is a Game with the unique Sport enum identifier being set to FOOTBALL
Game
A Game object handles all game related variables such as teams, period data, type of sport, and current score.
Hockey
Soccer is a Game with the unique Sport enum identifier being set to SOCCER
Master
Master class for Scoreboard, contains the command line interface methods.
Period
Period is an object storing period related data such as name, max amount of periods, length of a period and the current period the game is on.
ScoringMethods
List of available scoring methods the Scoreboard application can keep score of.
Soccer
Soccer is a Game with the unique Sport enum identifier being set to SOCCER
Sport
Sport is an enum which defines the different sports available to choose from alongside their associated stats such as period name, length, and types of scoring methods.
Team
Team objects store data related to a given team such as name, and current score.
